quran[32]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,"Uye avo vasina tarisiro yekusangana nesu (avo vanoramba zuva rekutongwa) vakati: “Seiko ngirozi dzisingatumirwewo kwatiri? Kana seiko tisingaone Tenzi vedu?” Zvirokwazvo, vanofunga kuti ndivo vanhu vepamusoro, uye vanhu vakazadzwa nekuzvitutumadza"
  25,22,"Zuva iro vachaona ngirozi, hakuna mashoko akanaka pazuva iroro kune avo maMajrimoon (vatadzi). Uye (ngirozi) dzichati: “Mashoko ese akanaka arambidzwa kwamuri.” (Hakuna achabvumidzwa kupinda Paradhiso kunze kweuyo akati: Laa ilaaha illaa illaah (Hakuna chimwe chinhu chine kodzero yekunamatwa kusara kwaAllah) uye akatevedzera mitemo yose"
  25,23,"Tichaenda kumabasa ose avakaita (vasingatendi, vatadzi), uye tichave tinoita kuti ave kunge guruva rakaparadzirwa"
  25,24,"Vagari vemuParadhiso musi uyo vachange vari munzvimbo yakanaka yekugara, uye nzvimbo yakanaka yekuzorora"
  25,25,"Uye (rangarirai) zuva iro apo denga richapatsanurwa nemakore, uye ngirozi dzichave dzinoburutswa dzakawanda, kuburutswa kwakanaka"
  25,26,"Humambo hwose hwechokwadi pazuva iri huchange huri wenyanzvi yetsitsi (Allah), uye richave zuva rakaoma kune avo vasingatendi (muIslaam)"
  25,27,"Uye (rangarirai) zuva iro mudzvanyiriri (mutadzi) paacharuma maoko ake, achataura kuti: “Aaa! Dai ndakatora nzira namutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)).”"
  25,28,“Aaa! Matambudziko kwandiri! Dai ndisina kutora nhingi nanhingi seshamwari yangu yepedyo!”
  25,29,“Zvirokwazvo akave anondishevedzera kure kubva kurangaridzo (Qur’aan) mushure mekunge yauya kwandiri. Uye Shaytwaan (Satani) munyengedzi wevanhu anotiza panguva iyo yekuda rubatsiro.”
  25,30,"Uye mutumwa (Muhammad (SAW)) achati: “Tenzi vangu! Zvirokwazvo, vanhu vangu vari kusiya Qur’aan (havasi kuteerera Qur’aan).”"
  25,31,Nekudaro takave tinoita mutumwa wese ave nemuvengi kune avo vanotadza. Asi Tenzi vako vanokwana semutungamiri uye mubatsiri
  25,32,"Uye avo vasingatendi vanotaura kuti: “Seiko Qur’aan risingadzikiswi kwaari kamwe chete?” Nokudaro (rinodzikiswa muzvidimbu) kuti tive tinosimbisa hana yako. Uye tinoridzikisa kwauri zvishoma-zvishoma, nguva nenguva. (Rakadzikiswa kuna Muhammad (SAW) mumakore makumi maviri nematatu"
  25,33,"Havambokwanise kukupa muenzaniso (wekupikisa kana kutsvaga zvimhingamupini kwauri kana kubva muQur’aan), asi tinokudzikisira chokwadi uye tsanangudzo yakazara"
  25,34,"Avo vachaunganidzwa muGehena nezviso zvavo, ichi chichave chidanho chakashata, uye kurasika kwakanyanya kubva munzira (yakatwasuka)"
  25,35,"Zvirokwazvo, takave tinopa Musa, Gwaro (Torah), uye takamupa mukoma wake Haaroon (Aroni) semubatsiri wake"
  25,36,"Uye takataura kuti: “Endai imi vaviri kune vanhu avo vakaramba zviratidzo zvedu.” Uye takave tinovaparadza zvachose"
  25,37,"Uye vanhu vaNowa pavakaramba vatumwa, takavanyudza (nemafashamu), uye takavaita muenzaniso kuvanhu vose. Uye takave tinogadzirira avo vanoita mabasa akashata marwadzo akaoma"
  25,38,"Uye vanhu veAad neveThamood, uye avo vaigara munzvimbo inonzi Ar-Rass, uye mapoka mazhinji evanhu aive pakati pavo"
  25,39,"Uye mumwe nemumwe (pakati pavo) takamuisira mienzaniso (sehumboo), uye umwe neumwe (pakati pavo) takave tinovaparadza zvachose"
  25,40,"Uye zvirokwazvo, vanopfuura muguta (revanhu vaLoti) rakanaya mvura yemarwadzo. Avo vasingatendi havana kuriona here? Kwete! Asi vange vasina vimbo kuti vachamutswa"
  25,41,"Uye vakakuona (Muhammad (SAW)) vanongokubata zviya zvekudzikisira (zvekunyomba) (vachitaura kuti): “Uyu ndiye munhu akatumwa naAllah semutumwa here?”"
  25,42,"“Zvirokwazvo, ange aripedyo kutirasisa kubva muvanamwari vedu, dai kusiri kuti takaramba takatsungirira uye takashinga mukuvanamata!” Asi pavachaona marwadzo, vachaziva kuti ndeupi akanyanya kurasika kubva munzira (yakatwasuka)"
  25,43,Hauna kuona here (Muhammad (SAW)) uyo munhu akatora zvido zvake samwari wake? Saka ungave mumiriri wake here (Ungave mutariri wake here)
  25,44,"Kana unofunga here kuti vazhinji vavo vanonzwa kana kunzwisisa? Vakangofanana nemombe, asi vakatonyanya kurasika kubva munzira tsvene (vakatonyanya kurasika kupinda mombe)"
  25,45,"Hauna kuona here kuwarirwa kunoitwa mumvuri naTenzi vako? Dai vaida, vaingourega wakamira kudaro, asi vakaita kuti zuva rive mutungamiri wavo (mumvuri unofamba nezuva)"
  25,46,Uye tinoudzora kwatiri zvakavanzika pashoma nepashoma
  25,47,"Uye ndivo (Allah) vanoita kuti usiku huve chiputiro chenyu, uye kurara kuti muve munozorora, uye vanoita zuva kuti muve munomuka (muzvishandire)"
  25,48,Uye ndivo vanotumira mhepo sechiratidzo chezvinhu zvakanaka pamberi petsitsi dzavo (mvura). Uye tinodzikisa mvura yakanaka (yakachena) kubva kudenga
  25,49,"Kuti tive tinopa upenyu kuvhu rinenge rakafa (raoma), uye tinopa (mvura) yokunwa kune mombe nevanhu avo vatakasika"
  25,50,"Uye zvirokwazvo tinova tinogova (mvura) kwavari kuti vagove vanorangarira (nyasha dzaAllah), asi vanhu vazhinji havatambiri kunze kwekusatenda"
  25,51,"Uye dai taida, taiisa muyambiri muguta roga-roga"
  25,52,"Saka usateerere avo vasingatendi, asi simbirira mavari (nekuparidza shoko raAllah) nekupikirira kukuru naro (Qur’aan)"